 to betray him unto them in the absence of the multitude.","year":33},{"id":"recfPYCfckmzjVsAM","ref":"Luke.22.7","text":"Then came the day of unleavened bread, when the passover must be killed.","year":33},{"id":"recYStPwxflNkp1JG","ref":"Luke.22.8","text":"And he sent Peter and John, saying, Go and prepare us the passover, that we may eat.","year":33}]}
